I've searched Aminet and other sources for a cheap and efficient mode to
connect my A1200 and a PC, but EasyLink (Parallel) is shareware and
crap. On the other side, EasyTransfer (Even 2.0) isn't that bad, and is
freeware, but it's still outdated.

As result of that, I'm going to try to code a modern version... Anyone
have ideas/methods to code serial/parallel? Anyone can code the PC part?
I'm not that good on PC :P

Another good idea, would be code a proxie-like conection to access INet
with both machines at one phoneline, but that would require an Ethernet
like connection...

What do you think about this, guys & girls? :)

cya




