Content-Type: text/plain

Hi Ott,

> > Is there anyway of just disabling the "Out of Bitmap" error and 
> > non-other?

> I think you're looking for the ClipBlit command here - exacty like blit
> but can be used for off bitplane blitting...

No, the ClipBlit function will clip the graphics which is exactly what
he doesn't want. He wants his graphics to be blitted out of the bitmap
on purpose.

All I can say is play about with the runtime errors and turn them
off before you blit outside the bitmap.

Cheers,

Paul

