Received: from boaz ([194.168.65.42]) by newmail.virgin.net
          (Post.Office MTA v3.1.2 release (PO203-101c)
          ID# 549-33929U100000L2S50) with SMTP id AAA7839
          for <blitz-list@netsoc.ucd.ie>; Sat, 3 Jan 1998 01:00:57 +0000
Message-ID: <34AD8BD2.4943@virgin.net>
