On 03-Jan-98, Dave wrote:
 
>  All a bit strange to me it seems like `BLITZ` isn`t shutting
>  down the system properly and then `AMIGA` gets confused, but
>  I`m probably wrong.

 Try going into Qamiga mode do your stuff and then End- and letting
Blitz shut down as much as possible always works better.

 This might help to flush the mouseport buffer after going into QAmiga:

  Repeat
    b=JoyB(0)
  Until b=0 

 
