Hi,

I have finished my HandBook program and it is now on my web site ( see
sig ). The full source code is included, so download it and have a look.
I'd like to thank everyone who tested it too.

HandBook shows you how to:

Read through directories
Find and open on the front-most Public Screen
Read and Write file comments
and much more.

I have also been playing around with the tabs.gadget BOOPSI gadget. It
gives you tabs across the top of your window that lets you change between
pages. I have put an example of how to use it Blitz on the web site.

Bye,
Alex

