Somebody wrote something about wanting to be able to "hide" some text in =
the
=2Eexe file!! This is text like: "L:MyProg.key". In my player i use Chr$(=
num) to
hide text like this!!

Ex:
instead of:
of=3DOpenFile(1,"S:MyProg.prefs") =


i have:
file$=3DChr$(83)+Chr$(58)+Chr$(77)+Chr$(121)+Chr$(80)+Chr$(114)+Chr$(101)=
+Chr$(102)+Chr$(115)
of=3DOpenFile(1,file$) =


I know this is a =A4#"=A4% long way of doing it!! But i think it's safe!!=
 And u
can't edit the .exe file :o)

Here's a file with all the Chr numbers!!!

Ses! =

