I hope you're doing
GetReg d0,the_address
MOVE.l d0,a0 (or LEA d0,a0)
JSR a0
..
if you use the BLITZ Call command, then you're in trouble cuz the 
registers are lost

so do
GetReg d0,the_address
TokeJSR Call


hope this helps



