> library I'm using have to correct it himself?

If the library is at fault then it would have to be fixed by the author of the
lib. This is possible but I'm sure Enforcer hits would have been removed
from the libraries already. Any Enforcer hits that are left are you're own
doing eg, Using somting like ReadMem 0,var,4 instead of ReadMem 0,&var,4
would read 4 bytes into memory location 0 "probably".. That would probably
do more than cause Enfocer hits but you get the idea!

Cheers,

Paul

