Received: from esoterica.pt (lis118.esoterica.pt [195.22.1.118]) by mail.esoterica.pt (8.8.5/8.7.3) with SMTP id XAA16966; Tue, 2 Dec 1997 23:40:28 GMT
From: Eduardo David <edavid@esoterica.pt>
