  |       Luca Carminati <toffi@spm.it>       |
  |       A1200/030/2+4Mb/WB3.0/1.2GbHD       |
  |                                           |
   =AF=AF=AF=AF=AF=AF=AF=AF=AF=AF=AF=AF=AF=AF=AF=AF=AF=AF=AF=AF=AF=AF=AF=AF=
