Subject: Functions Calls!!!
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain

Hello all.
I have a problem. Lets suppose that i have the following code:


Function 1{}
   3{}
End Function

Function 2{}
   1{}
End Function

Function 3{}
   2{}
End Function


So you are seeing what is the problem.
If I call function "1" Blitz gives an error saying that can't find function
"3".
If I move function "1" after function "3" then is function "2" that can't find
function "1".


This is a big problem!!!
Isn't there any command in Blitz that works like the command "Forward" in
Pascal ?


Can anyone help?

Thanx in advance,
Eduardo David



@ENDNODE
