On Sat, 20 Dec 1997 15:18:50 +0000 Dave 
<d.boaz%virgin.net@uk.ac.essex.mailhost> wrote:

>   What is the difference between Global, Static and Shared variables then.
> 
Global variables exist everywhere, without having to specifically 
say so.
Static variables are global constants.
Shared variables are only shared within certain parts of the code.


