X-Mailer: YAM 1.3.4 [040] - Amiga Mailer by Marcel Beck
Subject: GadTool Examples
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain

Hi all,

Now that my HandBook program is almost done ( if you're testing it and
haven't replied yet, please hurry. thanks ), I'm going to turn my
attention back to the FAQ.

This time I want to compile in one place all the info on using GadTools
gadgets. So, if you have any hints, tips, examples or advice on using any
of the GadTools gadgets, please send them to me.

Together with submissions from the list, I'll look through some of my own
code and create a definitive list of tags and how-to's for GadTools
gadgets.

If there is anything else you also think could be added to the FAQ, let
me know. I noted the ted.prefs one, so that will be included.

Thanks in advance,
Alex

-- 
