Hey!

I have this really great Idea for a Program! It's never seen on the Amiga (i
think). I have tryed to have a go myself. But im not that great a Programmer
yet! Then I talked to one of my friends with no luck! Then i gave the Idea to
Alvaro Thompson. He said that it would be pretty difficult! And now im sitting
with the great Idea and no one to code it. :o(  

IF U WANT TO HEAR MORE ABOUT THIS IDEA THEN PLZ. E-MAIL ME!!!!!!

Ses!
