Subject: GT Palette

I watched as Curt Esser entered 'GT Palette' into the terminal. "What's a
Syntax Error?" asked Curt

 CE> Would someone who has 2.xx workbench mind testing this and let me know
 CE> what
 CE> happens?  A screenshot would be best, if possible.  Or if not, could
 CE> you let
 CE> me know what happens, and if the gadget is displaced from the marks
 CE> shown on
 CE> the window?

Screenshot included from my A600P:

The little bar to the left of the palette gadget is the box that marks the
selected colour. As you can see, it's a little too narrow for comfort! :)

UUxT 3.0b UNREGISTERED Public Release

