X-Mailer: YAM 1.3.4 - Amiga Mailer by Marcel Beck
Subject: Re: GT Palette
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain

Hi Anton,

On 30-Nov-97, Anton Reinauer wrote:

>  Here's the grabs I've taken from my 500 under WB3.1 & 2.0- hope they
>help- Anton  :-)

Thanks for the screengrabs.  Just what I needed!

If anyone else is interested, using the following tag makes your GTPalette
gadget into a "mx" gadget on wb 3.xx, or puts an indicator box of x width and
the full height of the palette gadget on wb 2.xx

On 2.xx the entire gadget and indicator box are scaled down so it still fits
into the dimensions you specified and it won't mess up your screen layout.

x = (width of indicator box)
#GTPA_IndicatorWidth=$80080013
GTTags #GTPA_IndicatorWidth,x  


-- 
                                            Yours electronically,
                                            Curt Esser
                                            camge@ix.netcom.com



@ENDNODE
