Hi there!

   I`ve got a problem with the ListView. I have been making a program
   which has a GUI that remaps to the right colours if someone loads
   a strange palette but while doing this there have been problems
   in that some blitz commands ignore the colour numbers set in the
   screens tags lists. So what should have been easy has turned into
   a headache . 
    Most of these commands I have found ways round or used a similar
     commands which do what I want. But I still don`t know what to do
    about the listview which has a black background, there for I can`t
    see the Text, does anyone know how to alter the colours of a 
    listview?    
     There is a GTTAGs command with a colour tag but I couldn`t seem to
     get it to change any colours.


Thanks for any help

DAVE


@ENDNODE
