   I still haven`t found a solution to my problem that i want to find
the names of the samples in a directory: i tried something along the
lines of the following:

CHDir "Samples"

While MoreEntries
   name$(k)=EntryName$
Wend

  But it seems to do the CHDir ok, but it just skips pat the loop, not
finding any entries in the directory.... (and i did check there was
stuff in it!)

I then tried something along the lines of:

DEFTYPE InfoFileBlock fib

While ExNext_ (lock,fib)
    

Wend

but i don`t really want to use large libraries, and i don`t know the
structure of the InfoFileBlock type. If i knew this it would help, as
well as the whole concept of "Locking" directories....

thanks,
James





