I'm currently coding a CD player, and there's a "Program" mode that let's the
user have a pre-defined set of tracks to be played. There's a total of 12
choices. I'm using an array (*Dim List Tracks.Track(100)*) to contain the
first set of tracks - do I need to create an extra array for each new Program
List, or can I use just 1 array for each set Program list? Can someone give me
an example of some code that can achieve this?

Thanks in advance.

