Okay everybody here's the library that quite a lot of people were 
asking about a month of two ago.

It allows graphics and coloured text to be displayed in a standard 
Gadtools listview!  The example source code is NOT by me and a right 
mess so try and work it out.  This is NOT the original archive as I 
can't get to it due to technical problems on my Amiga (don't ask :-) 
) but I've put this together.

The archive isn't big so I've sent it direct to the list.

Cheerio,

Mike.
