Subject: Re: RTG support libs for BB2.1
Priority: normal
X-mailer: Pegasus Mail for Windows (v2.42a)
Message-ID: <85DCFD7089C@EXCELSIOR.MMU.AC.UK>

> 
> Hi!
> 	I've seen your WWW page but i did not find any RTG or GFX-CARD lib
> for Blitz Basic 2! Is there any? And where is it?
> 
There is no such library.  To support RTG or GFX-Card modes simply go 
through the operating system graphics.library using the OS commands 
offered by Blitz2 or directly using the amiga library commands which 
end with an underscore.  Paul Burkley on the Blitz-List can help with 
any GFX-Card problems as he has done it all whilst developing his 
kewl looking game 'Foundation'.

Cheerio,

Mike.
