the vertical blank period, doing nothing :-)   How do you make sure your
program runs at a smooth frame rate? Because if there wasn't much
happening onscreen and it didn't have much do to, it could render two
frames in one VBL, and you'd skip a frame.   

  Ta for the info- Anton 

-- 
      Anton Reinauer <anton@ww.co.nz>
      



