From: Andreas =?iso-8859-1?Q?H=E5kansson?= <andy@bjuv.mail.telia.com>
To: blitz-list@netsoc.ucd.ie
Date: Fri, 02 Jan 1998 01:23:42 +0100
Message-ID: <yam7306.2122.139970056@m1.418.telia.com>
X-Mailer: YAM 1.3.4 [020] - Amiga Mailer by Marcel Beck
Subject: ScreenTags
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=iso-8859-1
Content-Transfer-Encoding: quoted-printable


 Hello,

A few days ago I asked how I should do to open  a
screen with the following aspects.

  - Hires Interlace (640*512)
  - Depth 8
  - Undraggable
  - Disabeled depth gadget
  - Invisible titlebar

And I got a reply that I chould look up the  tags
in  the  Native  Developer  Kit  3.1 on the Amiga
Developer CD 1.1. And I did, and came up with the
followiing code to do what I wanted.

  Dim Tags.TagItem(5)

  Tags(0)\ti_Tag=3D#SA_Depth,8
  Tags(1)\ti_Tag=3D#SA_DisplayID,#HIRESLACE_KEY
  Tags(2)\ti_Tag=3D#SA_Draggable,False
  Tags(3)\ti_Tag=3D#SA_Width,640
  Tags(4)\ti_Tag=3D#SA_Height,512
  Tags(5)\ti_Tag=3D#SA_ShowTitle,False

  ScreenTags 0,"Test",&Tags(0)

  MouseWait
  Free Screen(0)
  End

And I managed to make most of the things to  work
by using the screentags, but I cant find any tags
to disable the screen depth  gadget  (The  screen
gadget  in the upper right corner, which lets you
bring another screen infront of the current one),
and how to turn of the titlebar.

I tried using the #SA_ShowTitle tag  to  turn  of
the  titlebar,  but  it  didn't  work. And then I
tried using  the  ShowTitile_()  command  but  it
didn't either work.

Does anyone know how  to  slove  these  last  two
problems I have? I open a borderless window on my
screen, and I can solve the problem with  turning
of  the  titlebar,  by  using  the windowtag that
traps right mouse button presses  (cant  remember
what  it's called, but it has the value $100000),
but that still leaves me with  the  screen  depth
gadget  problem,  and I whould like to solve both
of these things with screen tags if possible, and
not have to use the windowtag.

I whould be grateful for anyhelp that might solve
this problem.

 ByE!


-- =

=2E-=3D-=3D-=3D-=3D-=3D-=3D-=3D-=3D-=3D-=3D-=3D-=3D-=3D-=3D-=3D-=3D-=3D-=3D=
