ith it earlier but managed to fix it.

The question im asking u guys n gals is that how can i make the sprite lo=
ok proper if im using the following small code: (the cols are mapped inco=
rrectly)

;--

SpriteMode 1

Initcoplist 0,70,150,$1x414,8,256,0
Displaycontrols 0,0,0,$ee

Loadpalette 0,"Blabla",240

;---

The x (in initcoplist) means ive got it running fine with x=3D0|1 but i w=
ould like to use x=3D3 instead (for speedpurpose). =


