MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain


I know i've been going on for ages to find out how to do this......... but I
really need answered......

Me and Gareth are still trying to get this MUD server to work. Our problem at
the moment is:

How do we determine which user can be sent what message. By this we mean that
we need to know how to send ONE particular message to ONE particular user.
Unfortunately, Paul Burkey's TCP examples show you how to send message to ALL
users, not just one user.

Any ideas? We REALLY need this answered!

-- 

