Hello Blitzers!

I would like to control my demo to run at the same speed on all amiga(ie
faster amigas than my 28Mhz with 6mb ram)!
So there are solutions:
1) use med song to Control the program flow!
meaning when a sample is played then a TICK(time unit) has passed!
or
2) use interrupts (interrupt 5?!) so it will look like this

main function
check time(interrupt 5)  ; every 5th frame where 50 frames =1 sec!
bla bla
do something

end of main function

what do you guys think?
or is there an other way to do this!

I simply want to see if let's say 19 seconds has passed(on my amiga 19
sec= 19 sec on anyones amiga which is faster than mine)
Any ideaS?
thanx!
btw merry christmas and happy new year to alL!



