On Fri, 5 Dec 1997, Alvaro Thompson wrote:

> 
> hiya!
> 
> Does anyone know how to get WBDepth, Chip and Fast RAM, through OS commands?
>

Generally, to test Chip anf Fast RAM i use AvailMem_().

chip.l=AvailMem_(#MEMF_CHIP)	;only chip ram
fast.l=AvailMem_(#MEMF_FAST)	;only fast ram

chip_largest.l=AvailMem_(#MEMF_CHIP|#MEMF_LARGEST)	;largest chip
fast_largest.l=AvailMem_(#MEMF_FAST|#MEMF_LARGEST)	;largest fast

total.l=AvailMem_(#MEMF_TOTAL)	;total free memory

You must include amigalibs.res to use constants like #MEMF_???.
 
