I have a window with a pile of gadtools gadgets attached to it.  When 
I clear the window (for a reason) I want to redraw all the gadgets on 
it.  Is it possible to do this without a FOR ... NEXT loop and Redraw 
each gadget.  Is there a possible Intuition function.  I've tried 
GT_RefreshWindow but can't get it working.  I might be doing 
something wrong though.

Has anybody done this with success and if so how?

Cheerio,

