Received: (qmail 5774 invoked by alias); 6 Dec 1997 14:43:25 -0000
Mailing-List: contact blitz-list-help@netsoc.ucd.ie; run by ezmlm
Delivered-To: mailing list blitz-list@netsoc.ucd.ie
Received: (qmail 5769 invoked from network); 6 Dec 1997 14:43:24 -0000
Received: from server2.mersinet.co.uk (root@195.89.136.3)
  by orca.ucd.ie with SMTP; 6 Dec 1997 14:43:24 -0000
Received: from ebabes.mersinet.co.uk (paulebab@pstn106.mersinet.co.uk [195.89.136.26])
